cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving the decoding algorithm for neural machine translation models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a new algorithm that uses a universal score function and a penalty function, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning) likely categories as well. Additionally, since neural machine translation models are often used in computer vision applications, cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also a possible category. Finally, since the paper involves optimization and search algorithms, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category.
